  "description": "A spicy and velvety Vietnamese dish featuring red pepper, this banh mi is a nostalgic treat that combines the flavors of pork, pickled vegetables, and chili sauce, all on a crispy baguette. It is a raw-friendly and baked dish that is perfect for any meal.",
