  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together fish sauce, lime juice, and red pepper flakes.",
    "Add the sliced pork to the bowl and marinate for at least 30 minutes.",
    "Remove the pork from the marinade and bake for 20 minutes, or until cooked through.",
    "Spread mayonnaise on each baguette.",
    "Add the baked pork, pickled carrots, pickled daikon, and cilantro to each baguette.",
    "Drizzle the remaining marinade over the top of each banh mi.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
